entries.journal_entry_description: Investigate recent vandalism at the Coronet starport and bring down the perpetrators.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Speak with the Coronet starport master, Jesseb Convorr, about some recent vandalism in the starport.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Speak with the Coronet Starport Master
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Jesseb believes the Meatlumps are behind the vandalism. He recommends speaking with Finn Shallo, an editor at the Corellia Times who has been looking into various terrorist groups on Corellia. He could have more information on this kind of thing.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Finn suggests fighting some Meatlumps and see if you can find any clues to their part in the starport vandalism. You can find Meatlumps on the outskirts of most Corellian cities.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Take a Bite out of the Meatlumps
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Haha! Guess who's about to get blamed for destroying some terminals at the starport? Give up? You! Hahahaha! I hope you enjoy the CorSec thrashing that's coming your way.
entries.task03_message_box_text: Haha! Guess who's about to get blamed for destroying some terminals at the starport? Give up? You! Hahahaha! I hope you enjoy the CorSec thrashing that's coming your way.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Finn Shallo and tell him what you've learned about the Ragtags actually being the ones behind the vandalism.
